{
  "id": "csdn-article",
  "platform": "csdn",
  "mode": "article",
  "name": "CSDN · 技术博客",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "name": "标题生成",
      "type": "title",
      "needs": [],
      "promptTemplate": "csdn/article/title.md",
      "humanGate": true,
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "id": "content",
      "name": "博文生成（Markdown+摘要+标签）",
      "type": "content",
      "needs": [
        "title"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "csdn/article/content.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "use": "cover",
      "promptTemplate": "csdn/article/cover.md",
      "aspects": [
        "16:9",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    "review"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "正文用 CSDN Markdown 编辑器粘贴；首行 @[TOC](标题) 自动生成目录",
    "代码块标注语言以启用高亮；mermaid 图表与 KaTeX 公式 CSDN 原生支持",
    "摘要不超过 256 字，填入发布页「摘要」栏，影响搜索与推荐展示",
    "标签 3-5 个，选 CSDN 已有的精准技术标签（便于被检索与归类）",
    "声明「原创」并自查是否引用了他人代码/图片（注明出处）",
    "封面建议 16:9，含中文主标题、科技感配色，列表页缩略也清晰",
    "文末互动引导语已固定附加（点赞/关注/评论三连）"
  ],
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "aspect",
      "default": "16:9",
      "aspects": [
        "16:9",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "titleMaxLen",
      "label": "标题字数上限",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "30",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 80
    },
    {
      "id": "contentLen",
      "label": "正文/脚本字数",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "2500",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 4000,
      "step": 50
    }
  ]
}
